\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula ${\cal L}(A_{1}\times\dots\times A_{n})=\{I_{1}\times\dots\times I_{n}\}_{I_{i}\trianglelefteq A_{i},\forall i}$
\end_inset

.
